title: The Fog - Widescreen Unrated Version  (MKV)
description:
Unrated | 1h 40min | Horror | October 14th 2005




The inhabitants of Antonio Island, off the coast of Oregon, are about to unveil a statue honoring the four men (Castle, Wayne, Williams and Malone) who founded their town in 1871.



Director: Rupert Wainwright

Writers: Cooper Layne (screenplay), John Carpenter

Stars: Tom Welling, Maggie Grace, Selma Blair



Feature Commentary with Director Rupert Wainwright

Deleted Scenes with Director's Commentary

Feeling The Effects Of The Fog: Special Effects Featurette

Seeing Through The Fog: The Making Of The Fog

Whiteout Conditions: Remaking A Horror Classic

English & French Audio and Subtitles
